75-385.Division of Motor Carrier Services; established; Administrator of Motor Carrier Services.

The Division of Motor Carrier Services is established within the Department of Motor Vehicles and shall be headed by the Administrator of Motor Carrier Services. The administrator shall administer the affairs of the division.
